### Obtener todos los collectors
GET http://localhost:3000/api/collectors

### Obtener collector por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/collectors/1

### Editar collector (solo actualizar teléfono)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/collectors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "999888777"
}

### Editar collector (actualizar nombre y teléfono)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/collectors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Carlos",
  "lastname": "Pérez",
  "phone": "987654321"
}

### Eliminar collector por ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/collectors/1